metadata.name: Modry
metadata.description: Modry, an individual of undisclosed gender, is a descendant of a once prominent family that ruled sections of Neo-Tokyo. Born of royal blood, they possess a stubborn determination and an air of grandiosity, always insisting on their way. Modry exudes confidence and still possesses considerable wealth from their illustrious lineage. They frequently employ the services of travelers and smugglers, sending them on epic quests to recover the scattered remnants of their family's prized artifacts throughout the galaxy.
